{"title":"The Mavic COSMIC S 42 Disc Carbon Wheelset is $999","link":"https://theradavist.com/the-mavic-cosmic-s-42-disc-carbon-wheelset/","date":1728584207000,"content":"<p><em>Mavic introduces the COSMIC S 42 Disc carbon wheelset, combining performance, versatility, and durability at a price of less than $1000.</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1334\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/T3A0936_by_Dom_Daher-15.jpg?fit=1200,1334&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/T3A0936_by_Dom_Daher-15.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/T3A0936_by_Dom_Daher-15.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/T3A0936_by_Dom_Daher-15.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/T3A0936_by_Dom_Daher-15.jpg?resize=1536,1025&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1330\" height=\"2000\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/T3A0936_by_Dom_Daher-13.jpg?fit=1200,2000&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/T3A0936_by_Dom_Daher-13.jpg?w=1330&amp;quality=75 1330w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/T3A0936_by_Dom_Daher-13.jpg?resize=1200,1805&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/T3A0936_by_Dom_Daher-13.jpg?resize=768,1155&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/T3A0936_by_Dom_Daher-13.jpg?resize=1021,1536&amp;quality=75 1021w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"7735\" height=\"4059\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/DSC09881-cadre.jpg?fit=1200,4059&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/DSC09881-cadre.jpg?w=7735&amp;quality=75 7735w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/DSC09881-cadre.jpg?resize=1200,630&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/DSC09881-cadre.jpg?resize=2000,1050&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/DSC09881-cadre.jpg?resize=768,403&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/DSC09881-cadre.jpg?resize=1536,806&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/DSC09881-cadre.jpg?resize=2048,1075&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>The Cosmic S 42 Disc wheel, with its ultralight all-carbon rim, delivers instant acceleration and improved control. Thanks to a 21mm internal width, this wheel maximizes tire volume, increasing confidence, improving efficiency and optimizing cornering performance.</p>\n<p>A profile height of 42mm and wind-tunnel-tested flat spokes maximize the Cosmic S 42 Disc’s aerodynamics and give it lateral stability at high speeds. Cyclists looking for versatility on undulating or mountain roads will find what they’re looking for. Low weight guarantees excellent capabilities on the toughest slopes, so you can tackle the Alpe d’Huez like it’s a hill. Mavic’s UST Tubeless Ready technology simplifies tire installation, offering improved comfort and efficiency.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1997\" height=\"4000\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/F000786_0_Mavic_Cosmic_S42_Disc_Front.png?fit=1200,4000&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/F000786_0_Mavic_Cosmic_S42_Disc_Front.png?w=1997&amp;quality=75 1997w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/F000786_0_Mavic_Cosmic_S42_Disc_Front.png?resize=1200,2404&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/F000786_0_Mavic_Cosmic_S42_Disc_Front.png?resize=768,1538&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/F000786_0_Mavic_Cosmic_S42_Disc_Front.png?resize=767,1536&amp;quality=75 767w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/F000786_0_Mavic_Cosmic_S42_Disc_Front.png?resize=1022,2048&amp;quality=75 1022w\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"4000\" height=\"4000\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/F000786_1_Mavic_Cosmic_S42_Disc_Front.png?fit=1200,4000&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/F000786_1_Mavic_Cosmic_S42_Disc_Front.png?w=4000&amp;quality=75 4000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/F000786_1_Mavic_Cosmic_S42_Disc_Front.png?resize=1200,1200&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/F000786_1_Mavic_Cosmic_S42_Disc_Front.png?resize=2000,2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/F000786_1_Mavic_Cosmic_S42_Disc_Front.png?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75 150w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/F000786_1_Mavic_Cosmic_S42_Disc_Front.png?resize=768,768&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/F000786_1_Mavic_Cosmic_S42_Disc_Front.png?resize=1536,1536&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/F000786_1_Mavic_Cosmic_S42_Disc_Front.png?resize=2048,2048&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>High-quality spokes, durable bearings and the ID360 freewheel technology reportedly guarantee exceptional strength and longevity. Hand-assembled in Europe, the Cosmic S 42 Disc is the result of Mavic’s extensive experience in manufacturing high-quality wheels.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"5709\" height=\"3808\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/DSC09966-cadre.jpg?fit=1200,3808&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/DSC09966-cadre.jpg?w=5709&amp;quality=75 5709w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/DSC09966-cadre.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/DSC09966-cadre.jpg?resize=2000,1334&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/DSC09966-cadre.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/DSC09966-cadre.jpg?resize=1536,1025&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/DSC09966-cadre.jpg?resize=2048,1366&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Weight</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Pair: 1660g</li>\n<li>Front: 775g</li>\n<li>Rear: 885g</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Rims</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Material: 100% carbon fiber</li>\n<li>Height: 42 mm</li>\n<li>Internal width: 21 mm</li>\n<li>Drilling: traditional (front/rear 24 holes)</li>\n<li>Braking: disc</li>\n<li>ETRTO size: 622x21TC</li>\n<li>Tire: UST Tubeless Ready – Use with Mavic Tubeless Tape</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Spokes</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Material: steel</li>\n<li>Shape: bent radius, round (front and rear)</li>\n<li>Nipples: steel, ABS, black</li>\n<li>Lacing: crossed 2 (front and rear)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Hubs</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Body material: aluminium</li>\n<li>Body design:CLASSIC</li>\n<li>Disc standard: Center Lock® only</li>\n<li>Axle material: aluminum</li>\n<li>Axle size: front 12×100 / rear 12×142 – Convertible to quick release with adapters (not included)</li>\n<li>Freewheel technology: Instant Drive 360</li>\n<li>Freewheel: Shimano HG road</li>\n<li>Bearing technology: QRM automatic setting – sealed cartridge</li>\n</ul>\n<p>See more at <a href=\"https://www.mavic.com/en-us/p/cosmic-s-42-disc-rr2402\" target=\"_blank\">Mavic</a></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/the-mavic-cosmic-s-42-disc-carbon-wheelset/\">The Mavic COSMIC S 42 Disc Carbon Wheelset is $999</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"Josh Weinberg","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"e28b0147f424f26af2943190b8a2da11325f79a9f0d71cf444e0a400f326796a","category":"Cycling"}